title: Greek Lessons - Greek by Radio
description:
Audio course of 105 mp3 files plus 700+ pages of text notes (pdf) for learning Greek.  Please seed!

These are high quality 128k bitrate MP3 files - each lesson is about 15 minutes and averages about 11k per file.  If you cannot process these into smaller, 64k bitrate files and find the large size too inconvenient, post a comment and I'll make smaller versions available.
